OL,3,CBishop's Castle residents celebrate as
OL,4,Chospital beds reopen
OL,6,FTheir actions prompted the Shropshire
OL,7,FCommunity Health NHS Trust to commit
OL,8,Fto reopening the beds if a recruitment
OL,9,Fdrive was successful and locals joined
OL,10,Fforces with the Trust to run
OL,11,Frecruitment days into the new year.
OL,13,FOne Healthcare Assistant told me she
OL,14,Fsaw the campaign on the TV and applied
OL,15,Fbecause she thought Bishop's Castle
OL,16,Flooked like 'a great community' and
OL,17,Fshe wanted to be 'part of the change.'
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
