OL,3,CBishop's Castle residents celebrate as
OL,4,Chospital beds reopen
OL,6,FShe was one of many who applied and
OL,7,Fthe success of the recruitment days
OL,8,Fmeant that in April the Trust agreed
OL,9,Fto reopen the inpatient unit, to tears
OL,10,Fof joy from Bishop's Castle residents.
OL,12,FThe reason they want the beds so much
OL,13,Fis because the town is in rural
OL,14,FShropshire, close to the Welsh border.
OL,16,FIt's a good 30 minute drive to the
OL,17,Fnearest other community hospital in
OL,18,FLudlow and 40 and 50 minutes
OL,19,Frespectively to the acute services at
OL,20,FShrewsbury and Telford.
