OL,3,CBishop's Castle residents celebrate as
OL,4,Chospital beds reopen
OL,6,FPublic transport between the places is
OL,7,Ffew and far between and not everyone
OL,8,Fdrives. Therefore having some
OL,9,Finpatient services on the doorstep
OL,10,Fmakes a huge difference.
OL,12,FThat is now happening again from
OL,13,FMonday, with the expectation that by
OL,14,Fthe end of next week all 16 beds will
OL,15,Fbe filled.
OL,17,FThe people in them will be either
OL,18,Felderly people who need
OL,19,Frehabilitation, or people in
OL,20,FShropshire needing end of life care.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
