OL,3,CBishop's Castle residents celebrate as
OL,4,Chospital beds reopen
OL,6,FThey'll either be treated in one of
OL,7,Fthe four-bedded wards, or individual
OL,8,Fprivate rooms.
OL,10,FAll have been re-equipped, after the
OL,11,Fprevious equipment was moved to other
OL,12,Fsites when the unit closed.
OL,14,FStaff are a mix of newly recruited and
OL,15,Fthose returning to the site after
OL,16,Fhaving to go elsewhere in October 2021.
OL,18,FThey'll be under the charge of Ward
OL,19,FManager Amanda Houghton, a nurse who
OL,20,Flives in the town and who has great
OL,21,Fenthusiasm to provide a great service.
