OL,3,CBishop's Castle residents celebrate as
OL,4,Chospital beds reopen
OL,6,FFor the past two weeks she has been
OL,7,Fleading an induction programme that
OL,8,Fhas also served as a team building
OL,9,Fsession and she told me that she's not
OL,10,Fworried that they will suffer from
OL,11,Flack of staffing again, like they did
OL,12,Fthree years ago.
OL,14,FAmanda said: "Just looking at the team
OL,15,Fover the past fortnight when they have
OL,16,Fbeen working full time, they are very
OL,17,Fdedicated, they are very motivated,
OL,18,Fthey are excited that we are opening
OL,19,Fthe inpatient beds."
